title: Wind in the Castle
description: Twitter Roulette, Think Fast, Carson calls to ask Dave some questions for a job he's applying for, Worst Date Wednesday, we play "Get Lucky" - will we get lucky and eat a peanut butter bar or get Jake's dirty sock shoved in our mouth, The Movie Game, and more!
